{"tid":2461829,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"筆電挖礦請小心！中國用戶開挖之後 3 分鐘 VRAM 供電就爆掉了","createTime":"2021-03-25T15:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T01:38:59.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d86e1eba76fb9f837684a0a9f0b2bd8b35c810bb","tid":2461829,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"最近加密貨幣處於區間整理階段，比特幣雖有拉回，但依舊要 5 萬美元以上，沒有說跌非常多，也因此挖礦熱潮還是退不下來，再加上各大國外機構紛紛都看好加密貨幣，推出相關 ETF，後勢可說繼續看漲，這也使得越來越多人想嘗試挖礦，網路上也出現不少挖礦教學，甚至有人推薦家中有閒置的筆電就可以拿來挖礦，但這真的要想清楚。<br />\n<br />\n前陣子中國 bilibili 網站上，有人分享他朋友使用筆電挖礦 3 分鐘後就整個掛掉，無法再進到桌面，拆開看發現顯卡 VRAM 供電的 MOS 管已經爆掉，核心 100% 已經整個壞了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.zi.org.tw/kocpc/2021/03/1616393497-6cd0385740440d78d91ad483540060de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.zi.org.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2021%2F03%2F1616393497-6cd0385740440d78d91ad483540060de.png&h=a4d3f696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國一位用戶開挖之後 3 分鐘 VRAM 供電就爆掉了<br />\n<br />\n筆記本維修廝 bilibili 頻道前幾天分享一部「聽說挖比特幣可以賺錢，用筆記本挖了 3 分鐘結果電腦炸了」的影片，他提到，這位朋友找他維修時非常著急，希望能趕緊修好，因為慢一天就會耽誤到他發財。<br />\n<br />\n這位朋友說：「24 號晚上我看了一個挖礦影片，於是想動手一番，結果 3 分鐘後電腦就進入黑畫面，電源也被自動斷電，希望筆記本維修廝能把它修好，重振雄風，讓我拿回去大賺一筆」：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.zi.org.tw/kocpc/2021/03/1616393501-593e8dbd549ec4b16243091e8ca38b8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.zi.org.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2021%2F03%2F1616393501-593e8dbd549ec4b16243091e8ca38b8c.png&h=08df6283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先他把電源接上筆電，確認可以通電且開機，但一直無法進入桌面，而且會不斷重開機，他猜測該不會是挖礦把系統給挖壞了？：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.zi.org.tw/kocpc/2021/03/1616393504-f0610104980fe3b08639f12404663239.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.zi.org.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2021%2F03%2F1616393504-f0610104980fe3b08639f12404663239.png&h=5873342b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過拆開背蓋之後他發現，筆電接上電源後的電流有點太高，達到 0.07mAh，正常來說應該是 0.01mAh，代表說筆電有短路："},{"pid":"804c3d829bb1ac046efa639f96bad1aa88ff86ec","tid":2461829,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.zi.org.tw/kocpc/2021/03/1616393508-723ea5e7fd4da40eb2653a6154850942.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.zi.org.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2021%2F03%2F1616393508-723ea5e7fd4da40eb2653a6154850942.png&h=0ea35cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將顯卡散熱器移除後發現到，角落的顯卡 VRAM 供電左側 MOS 管整個炸掉，外觀非常慘：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.zi.org.tw/kocpc/2021/03/1616393512-fb6a7e6766a020ff554fc31f2a09a089.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.zi.org.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2021%2F03%2F1616393512-fb6a7e6766a020ff554fc31f2a09a089.png&h=5f1ef18a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然檢測出來沒有短路，但他 100% 確定，顯卡核心已經壞了，95% 旁邊 6 個 VRAM 記憶體全掛，意味著要修的話整個都要換掉，成本非常高：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.zi.org.tw/kocpc/2021/03/1616393516-01226bfc44e41a11487db3ecd367ddf6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.zi.org.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2021%2F03%2F1616393516-01226bfc44e41a11487db3ecd367ddf6.png&h=f448bf92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他也用吃飯原理來解釋為什麼會這樣。平常吃飯都是慢慢吃，細嚼慢嚥，但某天有一個人拿棍子，一股腦的把飯、魚肉和骨頭打進嘴巴，後果肯定是不堪設想。<br />\n<br />\n其實白話一點就是，一般筆電顯卡並不是針對這種超重度工作而設計，突然這麼加重這麼多，也難怪會爆掉。如果筆電顯卡是 RTX 3000 系列這類高階版本或許還可以承受住，但長時間下來其實也不太推薦，畢竟跟桌機獨顯相比，散熱還是差太多。"},{"pid":"f00f2126dcbec4bc079d95e0ef2558648bc8378f","tid":2461829,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">狂賀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1466f57ae92df4d9aa0ab6dbffc2d338226071f2","tid":2461829,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/375089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kocpc.com.tw%2Farchives%2F375089&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FqwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=2e96450a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/375089</a>"},{"pid":"bd182427b7b672361a7d69cd98d2dd1d0a213b41","tid":2461829,"uid":149844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"手機挖礦啲fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4f9246719a5533d1c0d6f2a25f42e007ee1088","tid":2461829,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6973a3426ed08776b31f0450994d6c4831430a","tid":2461829,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd182427b7b672361a7d69cd98d2dd1d0a213b41","tid":2461829,"uid":149844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"手機挖礦啲fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:32:52.000Z","msg":"手機挖直頭係scam, 迫你睇廣告"},{"pid":"ab20d1a70758d2973f7bbeb1fd6ffa5a8d210766","tid":2461829,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e6973a3426ed08776b31f0450994d6c4831430a","tid":2461829,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd182427b7b672361a7d69cd98d2dd1d0a213b41","tid":2461829,"uid":149844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"手機挖礦啲fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:32:52.000Z","msg":"手機挖直頭係scam, 迫你睇廣告"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2